Description: Toolkit to streamline biostatistics and clinical data analysis 
    workflows, covering aspects of descriptive statistics and exploratory data 
    analysis, sample size and power calculations, statistical analysis and 
    inference, and data visualization. Developed by the biostatistics team at 
    Laboratorios Sophia S.A. de C.V.
